    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6 and boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based <strong>hob-safe oven-proof casserole dish</strong> with a matching lid with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in 600ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[780ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.2L] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
