    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> cherry tomatoes </strong>and<strong> tomato paste </strong>to the dish with your <strong>roasted garlic paste</strong>,<strong> </strong>most of your <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
