          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>stock </strong>to the dish along with your<strong> arborio rice</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and bring to the boil over a high heat, then cover with the lid and put the dish in the oven</p><p>Cook for 20-25 min or until the rice is almost cooked</p>",
